WEBVTT

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:31.458
"Could you do that again,
but just this time, sound more Latina."

00:01:32.917 --> 00:01:35.226
"Um, OK.

00:01:35.250 --> 00:01:37.934
So you want me
to do it in Spanish?" I asked.

00:01:37.958 --> 00:01:42.583
"No, no, do it in English,
just sound Latina."

00:01:44.917 --> 00:01:50.375
"Well, I am a Latina,
so isn't this what a Latina sounds like?"

00:01:51.333 --> 00:01:53.934
There was a long and awkward silence,

00:01:53.958 --> 00:01:55.476
and then finally,

00:01:55.500 --> 00:01:59.101
"OK, sweetie, never mind,
thank you for coming in, bye!"

00:01:59.125 --> 00:02:03.726
It took me most of the car ride home
to realize that by "sound more Latina"